dfc2d75a4d551616bed772f18cd836d1563c455","tid":2301850,"uid":26385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"細個有過，維持咗成十年<br />\n試過曬啲偏方都無用<br />\n都係要入院打immunoglobulin先升一升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過幾個星期又打回原形，無限loop咗十年<br />\n結論：乖乖地聽醫生講打針啦，出面果啲偏方都係呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"維持10年咁耐 一定好折磨<br />\n打針果種係咪自費藥物黎?<br />\n但打完都係會反反覆覆 咁好似治唔到本<br />\n巴打而家好返哂定有keep住治療?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"我果陣唔係自費喎喎 公立都係收返一百蚊晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無計藥錢喎，而加應該都係<br />\n後期升返就無再理了，最後一次驗血血小板有一百咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係偏低但唔再有危險囉<br />\n係治唔到本架，不過都無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你要有心理準備會反覆架啦，短則幾個月長則好似我咁，要十年，甚至係lifelong<br />\n不過唔知可悲定可笑，你好快會慣出入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過好彩嘅係呢個病無直接帶來咩痛苦囉<br />\n唔痕唔痛又唔洗戒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf36bc423ac9655cf1638e0bd2c3e4daf87c37c5","tid":2301850,"uid":54471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859d1dd56931c31688b7841bf5e97471a5b0b395","tid":2301850,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7293faf7f822775d5e1765e69594b2daaafdf91b","tid":2301850,"uid":54471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddfc2d75a4d551616bed772f18cd836d1563c455","tid":2301850,"uid":26385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"細個有過，維持咗成十年<br />\n試過曬啲偏方都無用<br />\n都係要入院打immunoglobulin先升一升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過幾個星期又打回原形，無限loop咗十年<br />\n結論：乖乖地聽醫生講打針啦，出面